{
  "stem": "304.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And it was like half of the property, what belonged to my grandmother, to divide in 11 parts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And still, it was a substantial amount, because my father went to court and he won it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And my step-grandfather had to pay every time-- every month some money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I don't know the details.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But I think this brought it out that my mother-- her sisters and brothers didn't speak to her.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "The-- the half-sisters and half-brothers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And even after the war, till today, three of her sisters still are alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they very seldom talk about my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And they feel like an anger towards her and my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And I think all goes back to this part of her life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[DRINKS] So one of your grandmothers was-- raised fowl-- geese and ducks and so on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how she made money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they had also a store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A grocery store.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The grandmother was the wealthy one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The guy wasn't very-- he was a yeshiva bocher, a good-looking one.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she had a-- a store-- I don't know how you call it in English-- a [NON-ENGLISH], they called it at home.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wine, and liquor, and wholesale.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because next-- I remember the store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And next door was a store like a bar-- not as nice as here is a bar-- where one of the sons it was his-- my mother's oldest brother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was his-- his store that he selled-- he sold wine for people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like, for every Shabbat we went there for the wine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And also when the peasants came in, he will sell them a drink.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then later, under the Hungarians, we had a lot of stories what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I grew up with several languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
